procstep.procdesc:
This dataset was originally created as an ArcView shapefile and imported into SDE in January 2006.
Data Sources: Cass County parcel data derived from Auditor's Tax system AutoCAD drawing files (maintained by City of Fargo Engineering Department)
Process: Municipal boundaries were derived from plat information maintained in AutoCAD drawing files for the County. These files are updated as new plats are recorded or as splits & combines occur. A closed poly line was created of each city and imported in to ArcGIS.
New fields were created to maintain City name, Township, MCD code & quality of boundary line. A quality check was performed by selecting the unique Venue code for each city from the parcel shapefile. This two digit code represents the city that parcels ware located within and is derived from the Auditor's tax information. If discrepancies were identified further research was performed with the recorded plats & Engineering representatives for each City.
Updates are made based on new annexation plats.
10-22-10 - Prairie Rose city limits updated based on original incorporation plat. Line was previously drawn incorrectly.
